{"tid":2053513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥稱恒指收復「港區國安法」公布後「失地」","createTime":"2020-06-06T10:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T13:54:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"95a9351b175f937e2b6c7291b5883302680c939c","tid":2053513,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:41:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530579-20200606.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530579-20200606.htm&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=408fd2a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530579-20200606.htm&h=12b05e91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530579-20200606.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥表示，注意到恒生指數昨天收市報24770點，不但已收復人大公布「港區國安法」後的「失地」，亦是3個月以來的高位。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥在社交專頁說，接連有中概股回流香港作第二上市，生物科技公司用香港做融資平台，5月份採購經理指數回升，創4個月高位，香港的存款保持穩定，沒有大量資金流出港元或銀行體系等。<br />\n<br />\n她提到，中國人民銀行、銀保監會及證監會亦發聲支持，上個月連同外滙管理局發布《關於金融支持粵港澳大灣區建設的意見》，有利香港鞏固離岸人民幣、保險、融資及財富管理的業務，亦説明香港有穩健的制度及優越條件，可以經得起風浪。"},{"pid":"5ad73a0a0a9ad732d868fc79521e77500c47e5e9","tid":2053513,"uid":273703,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:42:22.000Z","msg":"on9 仔托住沽，輸死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3beee305ff6f519841268c9c5cc9c81fc81378","tid":2053513,"uid":38777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:44:38.000Z","msg":"到實施果日就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb0f6c307cb6f75c39f2a1a95d6ad5844c1cb0f","tid":2053513,"uid":9069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:45:19.000Z","msg":"財演"},{"pid":"c8961ca54ebbc010f7348f5a08545f7dcfc61080","tid":2053513,"uid":20898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T10:46:13.000Z","msg":"國家